title: 12Ghosts ScrSavMan [screensaver settings manager]
description:
ABOUT THIS SCREENSAVER:

12Ghosts ScrSavMan is an automate screen saver settings by
shortcut, scheduling or batch file.

Change screen saver, stop it with a scheduler, start with
password protection, set time-out (within seconds!),
enable/disable screen saver, set/reset password protection,
enter standby mode, change wallpaper.

This tool supports the Nutek power management standard, that
turns off monitor power when a totally blank screen is detected.
